              <li class="breadcrumb__item"><a href="/" title="Family-Friendly Recipes Everyone Will Love on Cooking Kitchn">Home</a></li><li class="breadcrumb__item"><a href="/recipes" title="All Tasty Recipes on Cooking Kitchn">Recipes</a></li><li class="breadcrumb__item"><span>Crispy Cabbage Dill Cream</span></li>
            </ol>
            <h1 class="landing__title txt-xxxl">Crispy Cabbage Dill Cream</h1>
            <p class="txt-l">Featured in: <a href="/categories/nourishing-salads" title="Healthy Salad Recipes Full of Flavor">Fresh Salad Recipes That Satisfy</a></p>
            <div class="landing__tldr txt-l"><p>Lightly crisped cabbage, tangy green onions, and a touch of Dijon mustard form a golden, savory pie fried to perfection. Once crisp on both sides, the pie is served warm with a creamy dill sauce that brings a fresh, herbaceous balance. The sour cream and mayonnaise base, brightened by plenty of fresh dill, make it the perfect complement to the tender cabbage layers. Enjoy this comforting dish as a meal on its own or as an impressive side. Feel free to add cheese for extra richness or adjust the herbs to your taste.</p></div>
            
